SUMMARY:Evening in Annapolis
DESCRIPTION:Crossover Day is one of the most important milestones of Maryland’s legislative session\, marking the deadline for bills to move from one chamber to the other. It’s a pivotal moment—and the perfect opportunity to come together in support of our shared priorities and the work ahead. \n\n\n\nThis is an exciting opportunity to connect with State Senators and Delegates in a relaxed\, face-to-face setting. No formal speeches—just good conversation\, light refreshments\, and a chance to make sure your voice is heard before the final push of the session.  \n\n\n\n \n\n\n\n\nRSVP HERE!\n\n\n\n\n \n\n\n\nI hope you’ll join us in Annapolis for a special Meet & Greet bringing together friends\, advocates\, and leaders from across our community. Your presence and support make a meaningful difference.
URL:https://mdgop.org/event/evening-in-annapolis/
LOCATION:An Evening In Annapolis\, 1 Annapolis St\, Suite 200\, Annapolis\, Maryland\, 21401\, United States
END:VEVENT
