SUMMARY:Cecil County's Lincoln-Reagan 250th Celebration!
DESCRIPTION:Come Celebrate with us at our Annual Lincoln-Reagan Dinner with a twist\, because we are also celebrating 250 years of American exceptionalism! Hosted by Congressman Andy Harris\, our Representative and Freedom Caucus Chair and our keynote speaker\, Chris Pabst\, investigative journalist and author of Failure Factory\, this evening is not one you will want to miss. Special guest\, Delegate Matt Morgan\, chair of the Maryland Freedom Caucus will also give us an update on what the Freedom Caucus is doing to combat the leftists in Annapolis. Enjoy a wonderful dinner\, cash bar\, networking opportunities\, opportunities to meet your Republican candidates for office\, and insightful presentations from our speakers. Sponsorships and ad purchases are also available for purchase. \n\n\n\n*You can also pre-purchase Chris Pabst’s book\, Failure Factory on this page. \n\n\n\n*All Republican candidates will get a table downstairs to display materials and one minute to speak. Each member of the team accompanying the candidate must be a ticket holder to attend the event.
URL:https://mdgop.org/event/cecil-countys-lincoln-reagan-250th-celebration/
LOCATION:White Oak Manor\, 1500 Chesapeake Club Drive\, North East\, Maryland\, 21901\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://mdgop.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/30/2026/02/37ab57bf-ad46-4ead-80ec-395a4ab7f9a6.jpeg
